title: Grateful Dead Live at Sandstone Amphitheatre on 1991-06-25
lineage: 16 bit – 48kHz DAT Clone > TASCAM DA-20 (SPDIF out) -> LynxTWO-B Audio Reference Interface (SPDIF in) -> Wavelab 6.0 by Todd Evans Editing and Mastering: Jamie Waddell on the GEMS Edit Station. Weiss Saracon for 16 BIT – 44.1kHz SRC and POWR-3 Dither Encoding by Dazed64. Tracked in CDwave, FLAC’d Flac Frontend level 8 Tag & Rename for FLAC Meta-Tagging.
description:
Set 1

Jack Straw  
Sugaree  
Walkin' Blues  
Candyman  
Stuck Inside Of Mobile With The Memphis Blues Again 
Tennessee Jed 
The Music Never Stopped 

Set 2

Scarlet Begonias ->
Fire On The Mountain 
Truckin' ->
Smokestack Lightnin' ->
He's Gone ->
Drums ->
Space ->
Comes A Time ->
Goin' Down The Road Feeling Bad ->
Good Lovin' 

Encore
It's All Over Now, Baby Blue
